title: ETH v1 Update: Raise $YGG collateral cap
body:
Intro: This is a vote to raise the collateral cap of YGG on C.R.E.A.M. ETH v1 market.
Proposal: Listing Committee
Rational: YGG is currently capped out on ETH v1 market.

For:
 Raise collateral cap of $YGG to 370370 or $2M USD. 

Against:
 Do not make any changes to ETH v1 market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
